title: The Finals Days...
itunes:title: The Finals Days...
description:
It's the final days before Christmas... The end of the Mayan Calandar... And Dog Watch Radio passes down the torch. 

We light up the new full bodied L'Atelier from the makers and creator of Tatuaje, and the all new medium CT-wrapped Perla Del Mar from J.C. Newman.
